title: Austin AND Round Rock Convenience!
posting_body: ['Property Listing# 802', 'This unique location offers you the conveniences of Austin and Round Rock!', 'With top-notch convenience, you are sure to feel right at home!', 'Close to many dining options, shopping venues and endless entertainment!', 'Close to Toll 45 and IH-35, as well as Mopac Toll!', 'Apartment Amenities', 'Six unique designed floor plans with nine foot ceilings', 'Two tone paint schemes', 'Crown Molding', 'Beveled Mirrors*', 'Ceiling Fans', 'Large Walk-in Closets', 'Linen Closets*', 'Granite Bar-Tops', 'Refrigerator With Ice-Maker', 'Black / Silver Appliances', 'Wood Burning Fireplaces*', 'Microwave', 'Oversized Closets', 'Fenced Yards*', 'Private patios/balconies with outside storage', 'Washer and Dryer Connections', 'Note: *Available in select units.', 'Community Features', 'Resort style swimming pools with complimentary Wi-Fi', 'Outdoor Kitchen', 'Fire Pit', 'Private Cabanas and Soothing Hot Spa', '24 hour fitness center', '26 acres of private jogging trails', 'E-Lounge', "Starbucks Coffee Cafe'", 'Outdoor basketball court and tennis court', 'Sand Volleyball', 'Multiple barbeque grills with picnic areas', 'Outdoor playscape with swings', 'Car Care Center', '24-Hour Laundry Center', 'Detached garages', 'Carports', 'Valet Waste', 'Storage', 'Call today to schedule your showing!', 'show contact info', 'licensed agent', 'Matt Davidson ~over 28 years of leasing experience in Austin~', 'Dash Realty', 'Dash Apartment Locating', 'Property Listing# 802', 'I have access to over 1000 listings, and can help you with all your renting needs!', 'FREE SERVICE TO YOU, NO FEES!']
